nodes.text: Queneth Li was a male Voss who left his homeworld to accompany the Mystic Talsa-ko, who joined the New Empire of the Sith Lord Darth Malgus at the behest of Darth Serevin. During the Battle of Ilum in the Galactic War between the Galactic Republic and the reconstituted Sith Empire, Queneth Li fought alongside Serevin when the New Empire's base at Fort Barrow was overrun, and was slain.

Queneth Li appears as a supporting enemy to Darth Serevin, the final boss in the Flashpoint "The Battle of Ilum" in the video game Star Wars: The Old Republic. Unlike virtually all other Voss, Queneth Li lacks a hyphen in his name.
